'''Voidfight''' was the slang term for a type of [[Starfighter combat/Legends|starfighter combat]] that took place in regions of deep space where the ambient light cast by nearby [[Star/Legends|stars]] was absent due to the battle's remote location. Because of this, visual scanning of targets and hostile fighters was reduced to almost nothing, forcing [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] involved in a voidfight to rely on other forms of instrumentation for the most part. [[Caet Shrovl]], an albino [[Shistavanen/Legends|Shistavanen]] Wolfwoman, was known to be highly-skilled in voidfights due to the nature of her condition.<ref name="I, Jedi">''[[I, Jedi]]''</ref>

